protein.general_function: Involved in transferase activity, transferring hexosyl groups
protein.specific_function: Mannosyltransferase involved in glycosylphosphatidylinositol-anchor biosynthesis. Transfers the first alpha-1,4-mannose to GlcN-acyl-PI during GPI precursor assembly
